XP System

Base points: 10 XP per completed habit
Streak multipliers: 1.5x for 7+ days, 2x for 30+ days, 2.5x for 100+ days
Perfect day bonus: Extra 20-50 XP for completing ALL your habits in one day
Coop bonus: Extra 5 XP when you and your partner both complete a shared habit

with each level increasement needed xp growth for 1.2x
100 xp = level 1 
120xp = level 2
